 beyond Kyoto, Washington, DC: Center for the Study of the Globe, Yale University; Brookings Institution Press.</p></li></ul><p class="c-article-references__download u-hide-print"><a data-track="click" data-track-action="download citation references" data-track-label="link" rel="nofollow" href="https://citation-needed.springer.com/v2/references/10.1007/s10584-021-03195-w?format=refman&amp;flavour=references">Download references<svg width="16" height="16" focusable="false" role="img" aria-hidden="true" class="u-icon"><use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#icon-eds-i-download-medium"></use></svg></a></p></div></div></div></section></div><section data-title="Code availability"><div class="c-article-section" id="Ack1-section"><h2 class="c-article-section__title js-section-title js-c-reading-companion-sections-item" id="Ack1">Code availability</h2><div class="c-article-section__content" id="Ack1-content"><p>No software used</p></div></div></section><section aria-labelledby="author-information" data-title="Author information"><div class="c-article-section" id="author-information-section"><h2 class="c-article-section__title js-section-title js-c-reading-companion-sections-item" id="author-information">Author information</h2><div class="c-article-section__content" id="author-information-content"><h3 class="c-article__sub-heading" id="affiliations">Authors and Affiliations</h3><ol class="c-article-author-affiliation__list"><li id="Aff1"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">International Centre for Climate Change and Development (ICCCAD), Independent University, Bangladesh, Dhaka, 1229, Bangladesh</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Mizan R. Khan</p></li><li id="Aff2"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">Department of Environmental Science and Management, North South University, Dhaka, 1229, Bangladesh</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Sirazoom Munira</p></li></ol><div class="u-js-hide u